<h1>So what's all of this about, then?</h1>
<p>Glad you asked! My Te Papa is a 'Web-based Companion App' for our Te Papa exhibits. In other words, it's a website that can accompany you on your smart phone, tablet, or laptop while you look around Te Papa, providing extra information, videos, audio snippets and additional material to complete your Te Papa experience. It can even make suggestions on what you might want to check out next!</p>

<h1>How does it work?</h1>
<p>My Te Papa uses a range of different technologies to make it as easy as possible for you to get more information about each part of an exhibition. You'll find NFC tags, QR codes, and unique ID codes scattered around Te Papa which will take you to each different section of the web site.</p>

